\left(\left(a_{1}, \ldots, a_{2}\right) \mapsto \left\{\left(a_{1} \cdot \ldots \cdot a_{2} \cdot \sum_{l \in \mathbb{Z}}~\left(l + 1\right)\right) = \sum_{l \in \mathbb{Z}}~\left(a_{1} \cdot \ldots \cdot a_{2} \cdot \left(l + 1\right)\right) \textrm{ if } \left(a_{1} \in \mathbb{C}\right) \land \ldots \land \left(a_{2} \in \mathbb{C}\right)\right..\right)